00:34:12,830 --> 00:34:14,620
in life?

878
00:34:19,180 --> 00:34:20,310
That's it.

879
00:34:20,870 --> 00:34:21,580
Bye.

880
00:34:26,950 --> 00:34:27,830
Hello,

881
00:34:28,310 --> 00:34:29,180
little Huan'er.

882
00:34:31,310 --> 00:34:33,220
I know you're probably

883
00:34:33,580 --> 00:34:35,700
panicking about not being able

884
00:34:36,060 --> 00:34:37,140
to find your goal

885
00:34:37,870 --> 00:34:39,100
and meaning in life.

886
00:34:40,140 --> 00:34:41,950
But Jing Xichi is right.

887
00:34:43,270 --> 00:34:44,540
Let's play it by ear.

888
00:34:45,270 --> 00:34:46,660
Life is not a test.

889
00:34:47,180 --> 00:34:48,540
There are no standard answers.

890
00:34:49,350 --> 00:34:51,020
Everyone will answer differently.

891
00:34:52,180 --> 00:34:53,140
I have

892
00:34:54,310 --> 00:34:55,020
my dad

893
00:34:55,830 --> 00:34:56,470
and mom

894
00:34:56,790 --> 00:34:57,580
around me.

895
00:34:59,540 --> 00:35:00,470
The people I love

896
00:35:01,577 --> 00:35:03,377
and the people who love me

897
00:35:03,620 --> 00:35:04,540
are all here.

898
00:35:10,390 --> 00:35:11,180
I'm very happy.

899
00:35:21,470 --> 00:35:22,020
(Song Cong,)

900
00:35:23,350 --> 00:35:25,140
(I remember you used to say)

901
00:35:25,911 --> 00:35:28,266
(that friends are meant
to be in certain phases.)

902
00:35:29,580 --> 00:35:31,100
(Do you still think so?)

903
00:35:33,620 --> 00:35:34,700
(Maybe some of our friends)

904
00:35:35,430 --> 00:35:37,500
(can only accompany us
on a short journey.)

905
00:35:39,430 --> 00:35:40,750
(But our lives )

906
00:35:41,830 --> 00:35:43,990
(are complete because
of this little journey.)

907
00:35:45,990 --> 00:35:46,870
(Those)

908
00:35:47,220 --> 00:35:49,020
(who have been in our lives)

909
00:35:50,350 --> 00:35:52,500
(will be part of our souls)

910
00:35:54,500 --> 00:35:55,660
(for the rest of our lives.)

911
00:37:39,270 --> 00:37:39,910
(Xichi.)

912
00:37:40,500 --> 00:37:41,500
(Huan'er, come out now.)

913
00:37:41,577 --> 00:37:42,755
(It's time to make dumplings.)

914
00:37:42,990 --> 00:37:43,540
(Let's go.)

915
00:37:43,700 --> 00:37:44,270
(Coming.)

916
00:38:08,270 --> 00:38:09,750
Let's go. Let's make dumplings.

917
00:38:20,644 --> 00:38:21,580
It's no use running.

918
00:38:21,950 --> 00:38:23,470
I'll be sure to get you on tape.

919
00:38:23,990 --> 00:38:26,270
None of you will escape.

920
00:38:29,500 --> 00:38:31,790
It's 3 PM today,

921
00:38:31,870 --> 00:38:33,470
17 September 2008.

922
00:38:34,755 --> 00:38:35,800
It's a beautiful day.

923
00:38:36,180 --> 00:38:37,310
The sun is shining.

924
00:38:37,955 --> 00:38:40,133
It's quiet outside the family
housing compound again.

925
00:38:40,133 --> 00:38:41,888
I wonder what everyone is doing.

926
00:38:43,310 --> 00:38:44,180
Li Tian

927
00:38:44,390 --> 00:38:45,620
must be studying.

928
00:38:46,350 --> 00:38:47,750
He's been trying to surpass Song.

929
00:38:49,555 --> 00:38:50,870
I sometimes want to tell him

930
00:38:50,910 --> 00:38:51,866
to let himself go,

931
00:38:51,911 --> 00:38:53,333
to stop being so hard on himself.

932
00:38:55,180 --> 00:38:55,870
Song.

933
00:38:56,990 --> 00:38:58,390
Song must be thinking about life.

934
00:38:58,990 --> 00:39:00,180
I'm really puzzled too.

935
00:39:00,200 --> 00:39:01,890
What on earth
does he have to think about

936
00:39:01,890 --> 00:39:02,870
all the time every day?

937
00:39:05,990 --> 00:39:06,750
Chen Huan'er

938
00:39:07,620 --> 00:39:08,750
is carefree.

939
00:39:09,310 --> 00:39:10,910
She must be either sleeping

940
00:39:11,140 --> 00:39:12,350
or having a good time

941
00:39:12,350 --> 00:39:14,060
because of something.

942
00:39:15,220 --> 00:39:16,180
Silly girl.

943
00:39:20,750 --> 00:39:21,950
If I could,

944
00:39:22,990 --> 00:39:25,750
I'd like time to stop right now.

945
00:39:29,140 --> 00:39:29,990
They always say

946
00:39:30,870 --> 00:39:32,750
that change is a constant in life.

947
00:39:34,500 --> 00:39:35,100
So

948
00:39:35,470 --> 00:39:36,750
houses get torn down,

949
00:39:37,222 --> 00:39:38,390
friends get separated,

950
00:39:39,870 --> 00:39:40,620
and even

951
00:39:41,500 --> 00:39:44,430
the closest people leave.

952
00:39:46,310 --> 00:39:47,390
But I always think

953
00:39:48,430 --> 00:39:50,270
that even if that day comes,

954
00:39:51,270 --> 00:39:52,100
the traces

955
00:39:52,950 --> 00:39:53,870
of those people

956
00:39:54,700 --> 00:39:56,020
and things

957
00:39:56,620 --> 00:39:57,830
will follow me,

958
00:39:58,990 --> 00:39:59,750
and accompany me

959
00:40:01,270 --> 00:40:04,350
all the way to a faraway place.

960
00:40:08,620 --> 00:40:10,140
Even if I've already forgotten

961
00:40:11,500 --> 00:40:12,750
this afternoon

962
00:40:12,750 --> 00:40:13,790
many years from now.

963
00:40:17,140 --> 00:40:17,910
Anyway,

964
00:40:20,790 --> 00:40:21,950
some things will change

965
00:40:24,180 --> 00:40:25,350
and some things

966
00:40:28,390 --> 00:40:29,310
will never change.

967
00:40:46,540 --> 00:40:55,100
♪I remember there's a place
I used to know♪

968
00:40:58,980 --> 00:41:02,340
♪Where the sun always shined♪

969
00:41:05,100 --> 00:41:07,220
♪The nights were warm♪

970
00:41:11,500 --> 00:41:15,700
♪Where we were living wild and free♪

971
00:41:17,620 --> 00:41:19,020
♪Hearts were bold♪

972
00:41:24,420 --> 00:41:27,700
♪But now I lost my way♪

973
00:41:29,940 --> 00:41:31,940
♪To get back home♪

974
00:41:36,420 --> 00:41:41,060
♪And I heard these echoes of my soul♪

975
00:41:42,665 --> 00:41:44,300
♪In the crowds♪

976
00:41:45,460 --> 00:41:47,420
♪It's been so long♪

977
00:41:48,860 --> 00:41:51,022
♪That I miss those days♪

978
00:41:51,066 --> 00:41:53,620
♪When dreams felt close♪

979
00:41:55,100 --> 00:42:00,020
♪In that place we called home♪

980
00:42:01,260 --> 00:42:12,740
=Always Home=

981
00:42:28,640 --> 00:42:33,810
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

982
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:40,680
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

983
00:42:42,450 --> 00:42:47,800
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

984
00:42:48,110 --> 00:42:53,600
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

985
00:42:56,190 --> 00:43:01,210
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

986
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:08,240
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

987
00:43:09,840 --> 00:43:15,260
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

988
00:43:15,720 --> 00:43:21,220
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

989
00:43:22,420 --> 00:43:26,380
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

990
00:43:26,380 --> 00:43:31,370
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

991
00:43:31,500 --> 00:43:34,930
♪And full of life♪

992
00:43:36,220 --> 00:43:39,680
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

993
00:43:39,680 --> 00:43:44,790
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

994
00:43:45,050 --> 00:43:49,440
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

995
00:43:49,940 --> 00:43:53,840
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

996
00:43:53,840 --> 00:43:58,780
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

997
00:43:58,780 --> 00:44:01,570
♪To know right from wrong♪

998
00:44:03,480 --> 00:44:07,010
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

999
00:44:07,010 --> 00:44:10,260
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

1000
00:44:10,420 --> 00:44:16,180
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

1001
00:44:16,600 --> 00:44:21,200
♪At just the right time♪

